OL,3,CStalking and drink spiking could
OL,4,Cbecome offences under new abuse law
OL,6,FIt is expected to be put in front of
OL,7,Fthe States for approval by the end of
OL,8,Fthe year.
OL,10,FCommittee member, Deputy Sue Aldwell,
OL,11,Fsays: "This significant piece of work
OL,12,Fwill go a long way
OL,14,Ftoward protecting victims of these
OL,15,Fhorrible offences and ensuring our
OL,16,Fcourts and
OL,18,Flaw enforcement has the powers to
OL,19,Fpunish offenders."
