OL,3,CStalking and drink spiking could
OL,4,Cbecome offences under new abuse law
OL,6,FThese new measures aim to protect
OL,7,Fsurvivors and their families.
OL,9,FThe Committee says it would like to
OL,10,Fget into more schools to spread
OL,11,Fawareness of domestic abuse and update
OL,12,Fexisting legislation to bring it into
OL,13,Fthe 21st century.
OL,15,FGuernsey's first Violence Against
OL,16,FWomen and Girls meeting was held in
OL,17,FJune with issues from domestic abuse
OL,18,Fto workplace inequality highlighted.
