OL,6,FDeputy Aldwell adds: "Joined-up
OL,7,Fthinking and multi-agency working is
OL,8,Fvery important to tackle the
OL,9,Fwidespread issue of violence against
OL,10,Fwomen and girls.
OL,12,F"We continue to partly fund additional
OL,13,Ftraining right across the community,
OL,14,Ffrom in schools to more extensive
OL,15,Ftraining for police and multi-agency
OL,16,Fteams on domestic abuse."
